HEADWORD: Silverbill
<hw>Sil"ver*bill`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An Old World finch of the genus <gen>Minia</gen>, as the <spn>Minia
Malabarica</spn> of India, and <spn>Minia cantans</spn> of
Africa.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

